DescriptionsMultilanguage.en: # Click on the Ice-shrooms to freeze the zombies
DescriptionsMultilanguage.zh: # 点击寒冰菇以冻结僵尸

DescriptionsMultilanguage.en: # Use plantfood for the Planterns to hide the surrounding plants
DescriptionsMultilanguage.zh: # 对路灯花施加叶绿素以隐藏周围植物

DescriptionsMultilanguage.en: # Plantern will make invisible zombies appear
DescriptionsMultilanguage.zh: # 路灯花会使隐形的僵尸现形

DescriptionsMultilanguage.en: # Umbtellaleaf will react to the falls
DescriptionsMultilanguage.zh: # 伞叶会对下坠做出响应

DescriptionsMultilanguage.en: # Buttercup will throw butter when gnawed
DescriptionsMultilanguage.zh: # 黄油毛茛被咬时会投掷黄油
